      "link": "https://so.html5.qq.com/page/real/search_news?docid=70000021_4486925ae4052352",
      "snippet": "元素获取与变换类 at() / findLast() / flatMap() 等</p><p>核心:精准获取元素､反向查找､数组变换(部分方法支持不可变操作)｡fmt=png&size=201&h=894&w=1080&ppv=1' data-aigc-mark='0'/></p><p>1. 正负索引获取元素&nbsp;at()</p><p><img src='http://qqpublic.qpic.cn/qq_public/0/28-1832734814-DFDF11135FFA162347D47FC35484A5A7/0?fmt=png&size=148&h=1058&w=1080&ppv=1' data-aigc-mark='0'/></p><p>2. 从后查找最后一个偶数&nbsp;findLast()</p><p><img src='http://qqpublic.qpic.cn/qq_public/0/28-191292768-67D352C455B8D2EC594E937FDCDDB402/0?fmt=png&size=118&h=1039&w=1080&ppv=1' data-aigc-mark='0'/></p><p>3. 从后查找大于5的元素索引&nbsp;findLastIndex()</p><p><img src='http://qqpublic.qpic.",
      "date": "2025-11-25 21:25:20"
    },
    {
      "title": "java 遍历方法 及 数组,ArrayList,HashMap,HashSet的遍历 - 草木物语 - 博客园",
      "link": "https://www.cnblogs.com/ooo0/p/7567009.html",
      "snippet": "1.for循环遍历 /** * for循环遍历 */ public static void forArr() { int [] arr = new int [] { 1, 2, 3 }; for ( int i = 0; i < arr.length; i++ ) { int j = arr[i]; System.out.println(j); }} 2.foreach语句遍历 /** * foreach语句遍历 */ public static void foreachArr(){ int [] arr = new int [] { 1, 2, 3 }; for ( int i : arr) { System.out.println(i); }} 三,ArrayList的遍历 1.for List<Integer> list = new ArrayList<Integer> ();list.add( 1 );list.add( 2 );list.add( 3 ); // for for ( int i = 0; i < list.size(); i++ ) { System.out.println(list.get(i));} 2.foreach // foreach for (Integer integer : list) { System.out.println(integer);} 3.iterator // iterator Iterator<Int",
      "date": "2017-09-21 09:56:00"
